; Regression test for issue #622: print must fully qualify all dates
; when a Y year directive is in effect, including bracketed dates in
; posting notes, so that the output round-trips correctly.
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/622

Y 2007

01/01 Test
    Expenses:Other    $10.00 ; [01/05]
    Assets:Checking

test print
2007/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Other                            $10.00  ; [2007/01/05]
    Assets:Checking
end test
